# ArcKit

**ArcKit** is an AI-powered toolkit designed for Solution and Enterprise Architects. It provides automated assistance in designing and documenting complex architectural structures.

In the context of the Data Platform, it serves as a peripheral resource for architects looking to augment their design process with AI-driven insights.